item.title: CVE-2022-42496|2024-08-03T13:10:40.970Z -- kujirahand -- nako3edit%2C%20editor%20component%20of%20nadesiko3%20%28pc%20version%29
item.description: OS command injection vulnerability in Nako3edit, editor component of nadesiko3 (PC Version) v3.3.74 and earlier allows a remote attacker to obtain appkey of the product and execute an arbitrary OS command on the product.

item.title: CVE-2022-41777|2024-08-03T12:49:43.800Z -- kujirahand -- nako3edit%2C%20editor%20component%20of%20nadesiko3%20%28pc%20version%29
item.description: Improper check or handling of exceptional conditions vulnerability in Nako3edit, editor component of nadesiko3 (PC Version) v3.3.74 and earlier allows a remote attacker to inject an invalid value to decodeURIComponent of nako3edit, which may lead the server to crash.
